{
  "stem": "24466.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There were horrible things were happened.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were so unlucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Wherever we went to a town, the bombardments was going on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we were flying, not riding the push bike, but flying, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I left Radom, I got some money in the [NON-ENGLISH], some banks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But everything was closed, and I went-- I left Radom without money, actually.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was very, very, very hard time for me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some of the schoolmates, my cousin, got some money and we were able to-- we was able to put through that bad time.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Horrible.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a lot [NON-ENGLISH], a lot of people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were leaving the places where they-- where they used to live, and just running away from the bombardment.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But they were-- with the [NON-ENGLISH], they were actually quicker than we are with the bikes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not so much on the road, but when we were trying to have a rest in the towns that we went through them, it was-- the bombardment was a horrible.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I end up, after [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] being in [NON-ENGLISH], being in Lutsk, in Kowel-- sorry-- in Lutsk, in Rowne.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was about eight or nine days for running away, we were on the border Poland and Russia.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The place was called Korzec.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-O-R-Z-E-C.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And a day before, or two days before, the truck that was signed through Ribbentrop and Molotov, and the army-- just when we came to the-- to that town, little town, the army, the Russian army went over the border and went to-- I asked one of the [NON-ENGLISH] that's a very hard characteristic, and I will never forget this too-- I ask him-- I will say it in Russian-- [RUSSIAN]?",
      "word_count": 71
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he told me--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How far you are going?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he said to me, [RUSSIAN].",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
